715017f-a.title: Manhattan: 109th Street (West) - Amsterdam Avenue
715017f-a.text:
221 West 109th Street, north side, West of Amsterdam Avenue.
This is a 1k-story and in the rear is a three-story frame house.
1932.
J. Clarence Davies Collection, Museum of the City of New York.
Negative No. 352.
